-- E3: `otherwise` guard constant — classify n | n > 0 = 1 | otherwise = 0.
-- `otherwise` in the condition position desugars to CVar "otherwise" AGlobal;
-- emitVar now maps it to "3" (the True immediate word), LTBool.
-- `__fallthrough__` in the else11 branch emits call void @mdk_oob() (provably dead).
-- main = classify 5 + classify (0 - 3) * 10
-- = 1 + 0 * 10 = 1
classify n
  | n > 0 = 1
  | otherwise = 0

main = classify 5 + classify (0 - 3) * 10
